I have found a solution debugging side by side mxnet.js github version and up-to-date version.

The solution was present in the past and is related to mshadow, see
https://github.com/dmlc/mshadow/commit/9105cd1c7ab4a50434bb5fdcfdff00d1719bc06c#diff-b24ff3303361719029d8b48321546c91
but it was broken by this commit
https://github.com/dmlc/mshadow/commit/c17a9af09b27a3df57e539080a0b618c735ac986#diff-b24ff3303361719029d8b48321546c91

So you need to change file mshadow/dot_engine-inl.h from line 434, inserting

> #if` MSHADOW_STAND_ALONE
> if (xpu::kDevMask == cpu::kDevMask && scale == 1.0f) {
> if (!transpose_left && !transpose_right) {
> dst = expr::implicit_dot(lhs, rhs); return;
> } else if (!transpose_left && transpose_right) {
> dst = expr::implicit_dot(lhs, rhs.T()); return;
> } else if (transpose_left && !transpose_right) {
> dst = expr::implicit_dot(lhs.T(), rhs); return;
> }
> }
> #endif

after

> Tensor<xpu, 2, DType> &dst = *p_dst;
